<div class="firstYear">
    <h3 class="titleArts">First Year</h3>
    <div class="desc">
        <div class="imageCollage">
            {{#each firstYear}}
            <img src= "/artsPortfolio/firstYear/{{this}}" alt="">
            {{/each}}
        </div>
        <div class="projectInfo">
            <p>This was the initial year where I have learnt the basics of tailoring and textile studies.</p>
            <p>The project of the year was called Super Volume and the inspiration was the skyscrapers and modern architecture like those of <a href="http://www.zaha-hadid.com/" target="_blank">Zaha Hadid.</a></p>
            <p>My inspiration was from the <a href="http://www.thegherkinlondon.com/">Gherkin</a> situated in London. I really was found of the weaving and roundness effect it had. I was also inspired by it during evening times where you would see speck of lights in couple of the windows. This lead me to create a fun reversible jacket in which one can see the day with the light to dark shading and the night with the speck of lights reflected as highlighted embroidery at the bottom. The collar is high to represent the slight suffocation a big city like London might have and the shoulders are rounded mirroring the curvature of the building.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


